Always read and follow the instructions in AI_DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md before writing any code.

Key rules to enforce from the plan:
- WPF namespace must be: xmlns:materialDesign="http://materialdesigninxaml.net/winfx/xaml/themes"
- UI Style keys: Input.Text | Input.ComboBox | Input.DatePicker | Input.TimePicker | Input.Text.Multiline
- Button styles: Btn.Primary | Btn.Cancel | Btn.AddNew
- DataGrid styles: DataGrid.Main | DataGrid.Row | DataGrid.Cell | DataGrid.Cell.Center | DataGrid.Cell.Actions
- Header style: Zone.Header.Primary
- Footer style: Window.Footer
- NEVER use hard delete — always set IsActive = false
- NEVER throw exceptions in services — always return Result.Success() or Result.Fail()
- NEVER use new ServiceClass() in Views — always use _serviceProvider.GetRequiredService<IService>()
- StaffRoleId belongs to Employee, NOT to EpisodeEmployee
- EpisodeDto uses ScheduledDate + BroadcastTime (not ScheduledTime)
- Dialog close: DialogHost.Close("RootDialog", true/false)
